<div style="background-color: #555; padding: 10px 5px 7px; margin: 0;">
    <img src="<%= @image_url %>" style="height: 30px; max-height: 30px;" height="30">
</div>
<h4 style="background-color: #34343b; color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 0 0 10px;">Welcome to <%= @app_name %>, <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name%>!</h4>
<p style="margin: 15px 0;">
	Your account has successfully been created. Now, all that's left to do is activate your account.
</p>
<p style="margin: 15px 0;">
	To finish your registration, click on the following link:<br />
	<a style="word-wrap: break-word" href="<%= @url %>"><%= @url %></a>
</p>
<p style="margin: 15px 0;">
	Thank you for joining <%= @app_name %>! We hope you find what you are looking for!
</p>
<p style="background-color: #d44; color: white; padding: 15px;">
	As always, remember: <%= @app_name %> will never ask you to send your password to us in an email.
</p>